Kubernetes Daermonset
====================
Daemonset are used to collect metrices from each node in the cluster.
node exporter is used to collect the metrices from each node.
This metrices are monitored for mantainence.
Daemonset ensure a pod runs on each cluster.

Tolerations is always at the pod side and taint is something which is applied at the node side.

 # remove them if your control plane nodes should not run pods
      - key: node-role.kubernetes.io/control-plane
        operator: Exists
        effect: NoSchedule
      - key: node-role.kubernetes.io/master
        operator: Exists
        effect: NoSchedule


